summary: Can Robert Downey Jr. please just buy the movie rights to Iron Man/ Tony Stark so that no matter how much time passes no one can...
body: Can Robert Downey Jr. please just buy the movie rights to Iron Man/ Tony Stark so that no matter how much time passes no one can ever attempt to play him again? Like no one should EVER even try to remake that character. Not in 5 years. Not in 10, or 20, or 30. Not even 50 or 60. Never. Ever.
